<p style="text-align: center">
<span class="PRTitle"><!-- NewsTitle.start -->Transcript of Senator Nancy Binay interview<!-- NewsTitle.end --></span>
<br /><span class="PRSub"><!-- NewsTitleSub.start -->Senate Session Hall<!-- NewsTitleSub.end--></span>
</p>
<!-- NewsBody.start -->
<p style="text-align: justify">Question (Q): Ano po yung masasabi ninyo na si Sen. Koko pa rin ang magche-chair dun sa probe tungkol dun sa carpark?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Senator Nancy Binay (SNB): Dun sa meeting namin kanina, we just wanted to establish na pwede ka palang humingi ng creation of a subcommittee. Siguro kami sa minority, if we feel na may mga issues o may mga resolutions na there's an urgency to hear e pwede pala naming hingin sa chairman na to create a subcommittee.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Pero basically Ma'am di kayo nag-object kanina?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Hindi, hindi. In fact ang tinanong ko nga lang is what is the process in asking for a subcommittee, kung kailangan ba ng formal letter or verbal na lang ba yun? Sinabi naman ni Senator Guingona, pwede namang verbal o kung gusto kong maging formal, I can write him a letter.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Given na po na ganun ang sitwasyon, will you ask for the chairmanship of the Malampaya?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Pag-aaralan namin sa minority, kasi if you remember, si Senator Jinggoy talaga yung nagpa-follow up dyan sa Malampaya Fund Scam.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Ma'am, may supplemental complaint na finile sa Ombudsman against your father, anong masasabi ninyo doon?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Ano bang content nung supplemental...</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: From P1.9 a yung kinita raw po o yung overprice daw po instead of P1.4 billion, P1.92 billion daw po yung overprice.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Pero based from sa NSO? I think my brother already answered yung question. If we go by the computation, kung ang basehan ay NSO, may mga proeyekto na "Parang sandali, may problema rin ng overpricing." Katulad nga ng na-cite nyang example, hindi ako naniniwala na if, for example yung Iloilo Convention Center di ba? If we follow yung presyo na sinasabi ng NSO, hindi ako naniniwala na kayang magawa yun sa P83 million lang na budget. So dapat tingnan natin yung competence ng NSO to say what is the exact amount na tama para makapagconstruct ng building o facility.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Ma'am may plano ho ba kayong pa-imbestigahan yung Iloilo Convention Center or kahit yung mga multicabs?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: I challenge Sen. Trillanes because this is not my advocacy. He started this di ba? Sabi nya, pina-iimbestigahan nya yung ama kok asi may balak tumakbo for higher office. If I am remember correct, Sen. Allan Peter already said na he also has plans, e lumalabas ngayon sa mga pahayagan na may allegations din sa kanya. So it's up to Sen. Trillanes to file a similar resolution kasi siya naman ang nag-umpisa ng ganitong advocacy. This is not my advocacy, yung gamitin ang Senado to put down a potential candidate for 2016.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Ma'am sabi ni Sen. Koko earlier na i-respect daw ang mga senators, huwag daw i-prejudge ni Mayor yung hearing regarding the parking building.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Di ko kasi alam kung saan nakuha ni Sen. Koko yung ganung conclusion na prejudged na nung kapatid ko yung mga senador. Ano ba yung context of the question kaya napasagot si Sen. Pimentel ng ganun?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Ma'am, mag-iinhibit pa rin kayo sa Wednesday?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Yes, kasi if you remember nagkaroon kami ng hearing dito sa Senado and we were accused, well majority of my fellow Senators were accused of lawyering for certain individuals. Ayoko naman na mabansagan na ganun din, unang-una, kapatid ko yung haharap kaya parang pangit tingnan na andun ako. I might be accused of lawyering din.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: (unintelligible)</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: A-attend? Kasi yung invitation is for Mayor Jun-jun so siya yung mag-aappear sa Wednesday. Yung mag-aattend? Ako gusto ko um-attend pero uupo na lang akong katabi ninyong lahat, o kaya sa gallery na lang ako uupo, pero hindi doon sa panel. So hindi ko alam kung allowed ba yun ng rules.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q: Thank you Ma'am.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">SNB: Thank you.</p>
